From: Mikita Lipski <mikita.lipski@amd.com>
Date: Thu, 15 Mar 2018 09:37:08 -0400
Subject: drm/amdgpu: Disable irq on device before destroying it
Git-commit: 088e7c16170645f1e2298ec6e0029079ef603635
Patch-mainline: v4.17-rc1
References: FATE#326289 FATE#326079 FATE#326049 FATE#322398 FATE#326166

Disable irq on devices before destroying them. That prevents
use-after-free memory access when unloading the driver.

